text: The ugly worm lizard (Cynisca feae) is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is found in Guinea-Bissau, Gambia, Senegal, and Guinea. ==References== Category:Cynisca (lizard) Category:Reptiles described in 1906 Category:Taxa named by George Albert Boulenger
title: Ugly worm lizard
